Package org.apache.wayang.core.optimizer.enumeration

Class PlanEnumeration

java.lang.Object
org.apache.wayang.core.optimizer.enumeration.PlanEnumeration
public class PlanEnumeration extends Object
Represents a collection of PlanImplementations that all implement the same section of a WayangPlan (which is assumed to contain OperatorAlternatives in general).

Instances can be mutated and combined in algebraic manner. In particular, instances can be unioned if they implement the same part of the WayangPlan, concatenated if there are contact points, and pruned.
